OL,5, Match of the Day host Gary Lineker will
OL,6, be "spoken to" after he tweeted        
OL,7, critically about the government's      
OL,8, asylum policy, the BBC has said.       
OL,10,FWriting on Twitter, the ex-footballer  
OL,11,Fsaid the language in which the plans   
OL,12,Fhad been set out was "not dissimilar to
OL,13,Fthat used by Germany in the 30s".      
OL,15,FA BBC spokesperson said the star would 
OL,16,Fbe "reminded of his responsibilities". 
OL,18,FHome Secretary Suella Braverman, who   
OL,19,Fset out the policy on Tuesday, said she
OL,20,Fwas disappointed by Lineker's comments.
